com.google.cloud.compute

Class DiskType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.compute.DiskType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class DiskType
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A Google Compute Engine disk type. A disk type represents the type of disk to use, such as pd-ssd or pd-standard.
    See Also:
    Disk Types, Serialized Form

      • deprecationStatus

        @Deprecated
public DeprecationStatus<DiskTypeId> deprecationStatus()
        Deprecated. 
        Returns the deprecation status of the disk type. If DeprecationStatus.status() is either DeprecationStatus.Status.DELETED or DeprecationStatus.Status.OBSOLETE the disk type should not be used. Returns null if the disk type is not deprecated.

      • getDeprecationStatus
